  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">MF2-04 Securing a Polynesian Promise for Climate and Community Resilience in Samoa and Tokelau</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Activity will reach at least 25 communities via schools in five Samoan districts and Tokelau&#x2019;s three atolls implementing environmental programmes and fostering a new generation of ocean stewardship and climate champions. It will increase understanding of critical marine ecosystems, climate change threats and mitigations as well as contribute to implementing ocean and climate policies and improve marine management through enhanced understanding and inclusive citizen science.</narrative>
  </description>
